title: UFYB 16: Love Yo' Self
itunes:title: Love Yo' Self
description:
I know the topic of self-love feels a little confrontational for a lot of you, but I want you to stick with me today as I share how it's possible for you to see all of your best qualities, be compassionate about your shortcomings, and feel amazing about yourself... without becoming a delusional narcissist. So pop in those earbuds and get ready to learn how to love yo' self (no positive affirmations required) and get shit done!

Get full show notes and more information here: https://unfckyourbrain.com/16
